<plot>Talent show which traveled to a different location each week to showcase young performers, with a winner being chosen by guest judges at the end of each episode. All the winning acts appeared at the finale to compete for the prize of $10,000. The winning act was 'Sly and the Family Stone' (qv). Guest stars from the world of music and comedy also made appearances.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?494802</url></doc>
